Package com.facebook.buck.features.rust

Class RustLibraryDescriptionArg.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.features.rust.RustLibraryDescriptionArg.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    RustLibraryDescriptionArg
    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class RustLibraryDescriptionArg.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type RustLibraryDescriptionArg. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
